📘 MONITORING AND CONTROL
👉 Meaning:
“Project chal raha hai usko check karna aur agar problem aaye to correct karna”

✔ Monitor = Track karna
✔ Control = Fix karna

📌 1. Creating Framework

👉 Framework = Monitoring ka structure/system
✔ Includes:
Rules set karna
Tools decide karna (Excel, Jira)
Reporting system

👉 Simple:
“Project ko track karne ka system banana”

📌 2. Collecting the Data

👉 Project se data collect karna:
✔ Data:
Progress %
Time spent
Cost used

🎯 Example:
50% work done
5 days used

👉 Simple:
“Project ki real information lena”

📌 3. Visualizing Progress

👉 Data ko graph/chart me dikhana
✔ Tools:
Charts
Dashboards

👉 Simple:
“Progress ko clearly dekhna”

📌 4. Cost Monitoring

👉 Check:
“Budget ke andar kaam ho raha hai ya nahi”

🎯 Example:
Budget ₹1,00,000
Used ₹80,000

👉 Simple:
“Paise control me hai ya nahi”

📌 5. Earned Value (EV)

👉 Important concept 👇
👉 Earned Value = Kitna kaam complete hua uski value

📊 3 Terms:
PV (Planned Value) → Plan ke according value
AC (Actual Cost) → Real cost
EV (Earned Value) → Completed work value

✔ Use:
Project ahead hai ya delay?
Budget over hai ya under?

👉 Simple:
“Kitna kaam hua vs kitna hona tha”

📌 6. Prioritizing Monitoring

👉 Sab kaam important nahi hote
✔ Focus:
Critical tasks
High-risk areas

👉 Simple:
“Important cheezon pe zyada focus”

📌 7. Getting Project Back to Target (Change Control)

👉 Agar project delay ya problem me hai:
✔ Actions:
Plan change karo
Resources increase karo
Scope adjust karo

👉 Simple:
“Project ko wapas track pe lana”

📌 8. Managing Contracts

👉 Client ke contract ko handle karna
✔ Ensure:
Terms follow ho rahe hai
Payment time pe mile

👉 Simple:
“Contract properly manage karna”

📌 9. Introduction (Contracts)

👉 Contract = Legal agreement between client & company

📌 10. Types of Contract
🔹 Fixed Price Contract

👉 Fixed amount
✔ Risk developer pe
🔹 Time & Material Contract

👉 Time ke basis pe payment
✔ Flexible
🔹 Cost Plus Contract

👉 Cost + profit margin
✔ Safe for developer

👉 Simple:
“Different payment models”

📌 11. Stages in Contract

✔ Steps:
Requirement discussion
Negotiation
Agreement sign
Execution
Completion

👉 Simple:
“Contract ka full lifecycle”

📌 12. Placement

👉 Contract final karna aur start karna
👉 Simple:
“Deal finalize karna”

📌 13. Typical Terms of a Contract

✔ Includes:
Scope of work
Cost
Timeline
Payment terms
Penalty clause

👉 Simple:
“Contract ke rules aur conditions”

📌 14. Contract Management

👉 Ensure:
Work as per contract ho
Changes properly handle ho

👉 Simple:
“Contract follow karwana”

📌 15. Acceptance

👉 Final stage:
✔ Client check karega:
Software sahi hai?
Requirements meet hui?

✔ Then:
Approval / sign-off

👉 Simple:
“Client final OK deta hai”

